Package com.squareup.okhttp.internal

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BitArray
    A simple bitset which supports left shifting.
    InternalCache
    OkHttp's internal cache interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BitArray.FixedCapacity
    Bit set that only supports settings bits 0 - 63.
    BitArray.VariableCapacity
    Bit set that grows as needed.
    DiskLruCache
    A cache that uses a bounded amount of space on a filesystem.
    Internal
    Escalate internal APIs in com.squareup.okhttp so they can be used from OkHttp's implementation packages.
    NamedRunnable
    Runnable implementation which always sets its thread name.
    Platform
    Access to Platform-specific features necessary for SPDY and advanced TLS.
    RouteDatabase
    A blacklist of failed routes to avoid when creating a new connection to a target address.
    Util
    Junk drawer of utility methods.
